{"tid":1178724,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚入]如果有一日女神同你講對唔住 你會點?","createTime":"2019-05-30T15:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T19:48:27.000Z","uid":47183,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc2c799d4c68eeb92693400a7372901d0b75cc7","tid":1178724,"uid":47183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:11:40.000Z","msg":"我地識左十年 當中有曖昧過 有親密過 但係大家都冇講出口 冇一齊<br />\n<br />\n後尾有d原因 我地冇搵大家 0交流左兩年<br />\n直至近排 好多回憶出番黎 <br />\n我下定決心要搵番佢<br />\n因為我唔想佢就感係我既人生入面不明不白感消失<br />\n<br />\n我見番佢 我鼓起勇氣問佢:「你係咪嬲左我所以兩年黎都唔同我講野呀?」<br />\n佢話:「唔係 我係嬲我自己沉船」<br />\n聽到佢感講 我真係好心up <br />\n<br />\n以前我中意放學留係學校溫書做功課 留到6 7點 <br />\n佢會等埋我 送我返屋企 <br />\n但明明都唔順路 明明學校直接有車返佢屋企個邊 <br />\n但佢都係會同我一齊走 日日都係<br />\n<br />\n佢去旅行又一定會買手信比我 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我呢?<br />\n一直接受佢既好 唔覺係咩一回事<br />\nsense到佢對自己好似唔係朋友咁簡單 但都同自己講「可能佢對個個都係感」<br />\ntext成日覆下又唔覆 ignore左佢<br />\n<br />\n我一直以黎都唔係刻意要收兵 <br />\n但宜家諗番轉頭 「你既行為 咪就係當緊人係兵囉!」<br />\n我好自責 見番佢之後 我晚晚都喊 <br />\n我喊我到底點解當時可以咁仆街 <br />\n我好想同佢講對唔住 <br />\n但我懦弱 我講唔出 我冇感既勇氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你女神同你講對唔住 你會點?"},{"pid":"a11960142ce3b00af01e6ea4a006ebf031677d68","tid":1178724,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"接受佢 繼續做兵"},{"pid":"467286805591929ce274a0a194321aa4b782ab01","tid":1178724,"uid":59192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"你一講對唔住<br />\n啫係承認你收佢做兵<br />\n啫係承認佢做左傻仔<br />\n仲衰過發好人卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d44eb1b608dfe4b5ac910575fb6a45c48cedb30","tid":1178724,"uid":6777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"下？姐係你係個女神？<br />\n自稱女神？<br />\n真係好委屈你喎dllm"},{"pid":"6159c84a7edba566c89f147fea1d48b69154f73b","tid":1178724,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"食咗佢啦"},{"pid":"faf02f83903f8ebfb6da08d76c915aaee46807ea","tid":1178724,"uid":23815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"感你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw <br />\n收兵就收兵 屌你老母 想講對唔住但又唔敢開口又係想點 ? <br />\n上黎懺悔完人地就無受過傷害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女乜撚野神  你憑咩自居係人心中既女神<br />\n<br />\n你都係想圍爐 有人同你講<br />\n&ldquo;唔緊要啦，你都唔係有心既&rdquo;<br />\n但 Sorry ，你FF下好啦"},{"pid":"67df6ba5927434c6ec026b4c701f97058d1ea1cc","tid":1178724,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"聽完對唔住咪算 毒撚係咪都無得屌㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d52ec2c8f34027807db0653392cce35a471beea","tid":1178724,"uid":119421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"睇完唔明 <br />\n樓主係無接受到個女仔<br />\n定樓主自稱女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bd1f1ac36396483d5c0da252becb8cbe5ef671","tid":1178724,"uid":14171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"你鐘意人咪同人講囉，男仔有人送上門<br />\n<br />\n你唔樣衰都好易受架啦，更何況佢愛你<br />\n<br />\n如果你唔鐘意佢，咁仲有咩好講，咪由佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df96f0704f7595891038afe699308e3c553ce282","tid":1178724,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T19:42:47.000Z","msg":"唔諗住有後續就咪兩年後先 say sorry啦"},{"pid":"c879dffa88e9fb7788e18935653285895bbef6f8","tid":1178724,"u